Context: The Centre for Construction & Engineering Technologies at George Brown College is constantly growing and evolving to meet the needs of industry partners. They offer opportunities for employers to work with their students and faculty to shape the future of their industry and community. Interested parties can contact them at ilotech@georgebrown.ca or follow them on LinkedIn (www.linkedin.com/in/georgebrowncollegeilo/) and Instagram (www.institutions.instagram.com/iloccet/). For more information about application deadlines, college news, upcoming events, tours, and other related content, sign up on their website. The contact numbers are 416-415-5000 ext. 4456 for general inquiries and 415-2000 for other queries. TTY users can reach out at 1-877-515-5559. For further college-related information, one can email ask.george@georgebrown.ca. The provided text states that the content on their website is subject to change without notice and should not be considered a representation, offer, or warranty. Students are advised to verify George Brown College fee requirements.
